data.description: **OFFERS WELCOME** This well-maintained home has a great elevation and curve appeal, as well as the interior design freshly painted and new flooring that features 5 Bedrooms, 3 Baths and a huge Loft with over 3000 heated sq ft for entertaining to include a downstairs in-law suite with a full bath.  This home is in the highly desirable resort style community of Lucaya Lake and has been well maintained and cared for throughout its ownership with fresh paint and new flooring. With a premium lot location, directly across the street from the property is the community park/playground and community amenities in a short distance. Private large L shaped screened porch to relax in your backyard. Once entered in the front door is the main living space with an open concept of the Living/Dining rooms and large eat in kitchen with the family room perfect for entertaining.  The kitchen boasts a large center granite island with plenty of cabinets and stainless-steel appliances. Upstairs bedrooms give you endless possibilities and ready to move in condition. The primary bedroom is large and can accommodate any size furniture with two walk in closets. The primary bathroom has plenty of closet space, a walk-in shower, large garden tub and dual sinks. The large loft is where family will gather, and then walk in laundry room complete the second floor with washer and dryer. Lake Lucaya is an all-natural gas community and features resort-style amenities including a clubhouse, 24-hour state-of-the art fitness center, Lake, Park, Playground, Pool, Sidewalk and Water Access.  You`ll also be able to enjoy the splash park, playground, 78-acre lake, and community dock that's accessible to all residents for canoeing, kayaking, and paddle boarding. Conveniently located near I-75, MacDill AFB, St Joseph Hospital, VA outpatient clinic, beaches, shopping and restaurants and only 25 minutes to downtown Tampa.
